some variations on the 99-bottles program

clojure.clj - a simple macro and a loop-recur
clojure2.clj - repace macro with funcion, loop-recur with trampoline
clojure3.clj - multimethod to handle the 0 case better; intentional overflow
               (what do you expect after too much beer)
               [now updated to format better, spell out numbers, etc.]

